Package: qtl2utilz
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for R/qtl2 and GBRS Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      'Matthew', 'Vincent',
      email = 'matt.vincent@jax.org',
      role = c('aut', 'cre')
    )
  )
Description: Common functions and methods for working with R/qtl2 and GBRS
    (Genotype By RNA-Seq) data. Enables importing GBRS genoprobs and read
    counts into R/qtl2 format, synchronizing and interpolating genoprobs
    across marker sets, and comparing GBRS vs array-based genotypes (e.g.
    MUGA). Developed in the Churchill Lab.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
